# Verse 1
{start_of_verse label="Verse 1"}
[D]Walking down the [A]long and winding [Bm]road
[G]Never sure where [D]home will [A]be
[D]Every step I [A]take, I carry [Bm]my load
[G]But your [A]love is my [D]guarantee
{end_of_verse}

# Pre-chorus
{start_of_prechorus}
[Em]And I know [A7]this much is [D]true
[G]Everything I [A]do, I [Em]do for [A]you
{end_of_prechorus}

# Chorus
{start_of_chorus label="Chorus"}
[D]Hold me [G]close, don't let me [D]go
[Bm]Tell me [G]everything I [A]need to know
[D]Hold me [G]close through rain and [Bm]snow
[G]You're the [A]only light in [D]this shadow
{end_of_chorus}

{chorus}

# Verse 2
{start_of_verse label="Verse 2"}
[D]Through the [A]fire and the [Bm]flood
[G]You have [D]never left my [A]side
[D]In my [A]veins runs more than [Bm]blood
[G]It's your [A]love my [D]guide
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_prechorus}
[Em]And I know [A7]this much is [D]true
[G]Everything I [A]do, I [Em]do for [A]you
{end_of_prechorus}

{chorus}

# Bridge
{start_of_bridge}
[F#m]When I [Bm]lose my way
[Em]I'll [A]find my way [D]home
[F#m]Through [Bm]night and day
[Em]I'm [A]never a[D]lone
{end_of_bridge}

{chorus}

